  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Healthcare to 12,000 poor in rural Bangalore</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project takes healthcare to the doorstep of the poor in rural villages of Bangalore, through e-consultations.  We provide medical care to women, children, the elderly and persons with disabilities. Our trained healthcare workers perform BP measurements, test GRBs tests. Depending on the readings, they connect the doctors at our hospital. and medicines are distributed.  Our e-mobile clinics works well for chronic diseases and acts as an effective triaging system for hospital referrals.</narrative>
  </description>
